{"id":234,"parent_id":224,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":234,"title":"Hebrews 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"Heb.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","We are sanctified by the shedding of the blood of Christ—The superiority of His sacrifice is explained—Those who fall from grace through willful sin are damned—The just will live by faith."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.1","order":"03.21.010.24163"},["b","1"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"law"],"having a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"shadow"],"of good things to come,",["i","and"],"not the very image of the things, can never with those sacrifices which they offered",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"year"],"by year continually make the comers thereunto perfect."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.2","order":"03.21.010.24164"},["b","2"],"For then would they not have ceased to be offered? because that the worshippers once",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"purged"],"should have had no more",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"conscience"],"of sins."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.3","order":"03.21.010.24165"},["b","3"],"But in those",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sacrifices"],"there is"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"remembrance"],"again",["i","made"],"of sins every year."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.4","order":"03.21.010.24166"},["b","4"],"For",["i","it is"],"not possible that the blood of bulls and of goats should take away sins."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.5","order":"03.21.010.24167"},["b","5"],"Wherefore when he cometh into the world, he saith, Sacrifice and offering thou wouldest not, but a body hast thou prepared me:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.6","order":"03.21.010.24168"},["b","6"],"In burnt offerings and",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"sacrifices"]],"for sin thou hast had no pleasure."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.7","order":"03.21.010.24169"},["b","7"],"Then said I, Lo, I come (in the volume of the book it is written of me,) to do thy will, O God."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.8","order":"03.21.010.24170"},["b","8"],"Above when he said, Sacrifice and offering and burnt offerings and",["i","offering"],"for sin thou wouldest not, neither hadst pleasure",["i","therein;"],"which are offered by the law;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.9","order":"03.21.010.24171"},["b","9"],"Then said he, Lo, I come to do thy will, O God. He taketh away the first, that he may establish the second."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.10","order":"03.21.010.24172"},["b","10"],"By the which will we are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"sanctified"],"through the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"offering"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"of"],"the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"body"],"of Jesus Christ",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"once"],["i","for all."]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.11","order":"03.21.010.24173"},["b","11"],"And every priest standeth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"daily"],"ministering and offering oftentimes the same sacrifices, which can never take away",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"sins"],":"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.12","order":"03.21.010.24174"},["b","12"],"But this man, after he had offered one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"sacrifice"],"for sins for ever, sat down on the right hand of God;"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.13","order":"03.21.010.24175"},["b","13"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"From"],"henceforth expecting till his enemies be made his footstool."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.14","order":"03.21.010.24176"},["b","14"],"For by one offering he hath perfected for ever them that are sanctified."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.15","order":"03.21.010.24177"},["b","15"],["i","Whereof"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Holy Ghost"],"also is a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"witness"],"to us: for after that he had said before,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.16","order":"03.21.010.24178"},["b","16"],"This",["i","is"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"covenant"],"that I will make with them after those days, saith the Lord, I will put my laws into their hearts, and in their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"minds"],"will I write them;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.17","order":"03.21.010.24179"},["b","17"],"And their sins and iniquities will I remember no more."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.18","order":"03.21.010.24180"},["b","18"],"Now where",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"remission"],"of these",["i","is, there is"],"no more offering for sin."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.19","order":"03.21.010.24181"},["b","19"],"Having therefore, brethren,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"boldness"],"to enter into the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"holiest"],"by the blood of Jesus,"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.20","order":"03.21.010.24182"},["b","20"],"By a new and living way, which he hath consecrated for us, through the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"veil"],", that is to say, his flesh;"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.21","order":"03.21.010.24183"},["b","21"],"And",["i","having"],"an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"high priest"],"over the house of God;"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.22","order":"03.21.010.24184"},["b","22"],"Let us",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"draw"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"near"],"with a true heart in full assurance of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"faith"],", having our hearts",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_22d"},"sprinkled"],"from an evil",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_22e"},"conscience"],", and our bodies washed with pure water."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.23","order":"03.21.010.24185"},["b","23"],"Let us hold fast the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"profession"],"of",["i","our"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"faith"],"without wavering; (for he",["i","is"],"faithful that promised;)"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.24","order":"03.21.010.24186"},["b","24"],"And let us",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"consider"],"one another to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"provoke"],"unto love and to good works:"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.25","order":"03.21.010.24187"},["b","25"],"Not forsaking the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"assembling"],"of ourselves together, as the manner of some",["i","is;"],"but exhorting",["i","one another:"],"and so much the more, as ye see the day approaching."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.26","order":"03.21.010.24188"},["b","26"],"For if we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"sin"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"wilfully"],"after that we have received the knowledge of the truth, there remaineth no more sacrifice for sins,"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.27","order":"03.21.010.24189"},["b","27"],"But a certain fearful looking for of judgment and fiery",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"indignation"],", which shall devour the adversaries."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.28","order":"03.21.010.24190"},["b","28"],"He that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"despised"],"Moses’ law died without mercy under two or three witnesses:"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.29","order":"03.21.010.24191"},["b","29"],"Of how much sorer",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"punishment"],", suppose ye, shall he be thought worthy, who hath trodden under foot the Son of God, and hath counted the blood of the covenant, wherewith he was sanctified, an unholy thing, and hath done",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"despite"],"unto the Spirit of grace?"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.30","order":"03.21.010.24192"},["b","30"],"For we know him that hath said,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"Vengeance"],["i","belongeth"],"unto me, I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"recompense"],", saith the Lord. And again, The Lord shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_30c"},"judge"],"his people."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.31","order":"03.21.010.24193"},["b","31"],["i","It is"],"a fearful thing to fall into the hands of the living God."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.32","order":"03.21.010.24194"},["b","32"],"But call to remembrance the former days, in which, after ye were illuminated, ye endured a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"fight"],"of afflictions;"],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.33","order":"03.21.010.24195"},["b","33"],"Partly, whilst ye were made a gazingstock both by reproaches and afflictions; and partly, whilst ye became companions of them that were so used."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.34","order":"03.21.010.24196"},["b","34"],"For ye had compassion of me in my bonds, and took",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"joyfully"],"the spoiling of your goods, knowing in yourselves that ye have in heaven a better and an enduring",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"substance"],"."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.35","order":"03.21.010.24197"},["b","35"],"Cast not away therefore your confidence, which hath great recompence of reward."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.36","order":"03.21.010.24198"},["b","36"],"For ye have need of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"patience"],", that, after ye have done the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"will"],"of God, ye might receive the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_36c"},"promise"],"."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.37","order":"03.21.010.24199"},["b","37"],"For yet a little while, and he that shall come will come, and will not tarry."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.38","order":"03.21.010.24200"},["b","38"],"Now the just shall live by faith: but if",["i","any man"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"draw back"],", my soul shall have no pleasure in him."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.39","order":"03.21.010.24201"},["b","39"],"But we are not of them who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"draw back"],"unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_39b"},"perdition"],"; but of them that believe to the saving of the soul."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.1a","order":"03.21.010.24202"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.15.14-15"},"Mosiah 3:15 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.28.28-32"},"13:28 (28–32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.1b","order":"03.21.010.24204"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/symbolism"},"Symbolism"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.1c","order":"03.21.010.24206"},["b","1c"],["span.small","JST"],"Heb. 10:1 …",["i","continually"],"year by year make …"],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.2a","order":"03.21.010.24208"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"TG Remission of Sins"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.2b","order":"03.21.010.24210"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"TG Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.3a","order":"03.21.010.24212"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"TG Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.3b","order":"03.21.010.24214"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/16.21"},"Lev. 16:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.7"},"Heb. 9:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.6a","order":"03.21.010.24216"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/15.22"},"1 Sam. 15:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/6.7"},"Micah 6:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.10a","order":"03.21.010.24218"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sanctification"},"TG Sanctification"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.10b","order":"03.21.010.24220"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.10c","order":"03.21.010.24222"},["b","10c"],["span.small","JST"],"Heb. 10:10 …",["i","once"],"of the body of Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.10d","order":"03.21.010.24224"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/6.51"},"John 6:51"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.12"},"Heb. 9:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"10e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.10e","order":"03.21.010.24226"},["b","10e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.10"},"Rom. 6:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.11a","order":"03.21.010.24228"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/7.27"},"Heb. 7:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.11b","order":"03.21.010.24230"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/4.20.20,26"},"Lev. 4:20 (20, 26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.12a","order":"03.21.010.24232"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"TG Sacrifice"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-sacrifice"},"Self-Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.13a","order":"03.21.010.24234"},["b","13a"],["span.small","JST"],"Heb. 10:13 From henceforth",["i","to reign until"],"his enemies …"],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.15a","order":"03.21.010.24236"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/3.7"},"Heb. 3:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.15b","order":"03.21.010.24238"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Mission of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.16a","order":"03.21.010.24240"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/59.21.20-21"},"Isa. 59:21 (20–21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/11.27"},"Rom. 11:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.9.5-9"},"D&C 49:9 (5–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.16b","order":"03.21.010.24242"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/31.31-33"},"Jer. 31:31–33"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.18a","order":"03.21.010.24244"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"TG Remission of Sins"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.19a","order":"03.21.010.24246"},["b","19a"],["span.small","GR"],"license, authority."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.19b","order":"03.21.010.24248"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/16.2.2-4"},"Lev. 16:2 (2–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.12"},"Heb. 9:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.20a","order":"03.21.010.24250"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/veil"},"TG Veil"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.21a","order":"03.21.010.24252"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/high-priest-melchizedek-priesthood"},"TG High Priest, Melchizedek Priesthood"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/heb/10.22a","order":"03